lead_paragraph: Cardinals ace Adam Wainwright struggled with his focus in his first start since last April and Matt Holliday made his professional debut at first base Monday as St. Louis beat a New York Mets split squad 9-4.

headline.print_headline: Wainwright Wilder Than Usual in Spring Debut, Cards Top Mets
